# .dockerignore Challenge of the Day - Joshua Higginson - 12th August 2020

# Ignore:
# ...any files ending in ".md"
*.md

# ...any files in the directory of src
*/src/*

# ...Any files beginning with "foo" EXCEPT if they also begin with "bar"

foo!(bar)*


# Starts with FOO, except if it also ends with bar.

foo*!*bar


# ...Any files ending in ".txt" but only in directories that start with the letter "a".

/a*.txt



